  notify the Directorate General Human Resources in writing without
  delay. (ECB Staff Rules, p.63.)  5. Related detail: The household
  allowance shall not be less than EUR 345 per month. If both
  spouses/recognised partners are ECB staff and both earn less than
  the limit, the allowance is paid to the member of staff with the
  higher salary. (ECB Conditions of Employment, p.9; ECB Staff Rules,
  p.63.)  (ECB Conditions of Employment, p.9; ECB Staff Rules, p.63)
